fields.name: src_straight_through_processing_rule_row_md5checksum
fields.expression:
MD5(
'condition_schema_name_left' || src_condition_schema_name_left ||
'condition_object_name_left' || src_condition_object_name_left || 
'condition_column_name_left' || src_condition_column_name_left || 
'calculation_operator' || src_calculation_operator || 
'condition_schema_name_right' || src_condition_schema_name_right || 
'condition_object_name_right' || src_condition_object_name_right || 
'condition_column_name_right' || src_condition_column_name_right ||
'calculation_constant_value' || src_calculation_constant_value || 
'comparative_operator' || src_comparative_operator ||
'comparative_type' || src_comparative_type || 
'threshold_value' || src_threshold_value || 
'logical_operator' || src_logical_operator || 
'action_flag' || src_action_flag || 
'priority_order_number' || src_priority_order_number || 
'rule_created_by' || src_rule_created_by || 
'rule_updated_by' || src_rule_updated_by 
)

object.customQuery:
SELECT 
    straight_through_processing_rule_row_id as tgt_straight_through_processing_rule_row_id, 
    straight_through_processing_rule_row_md5checksum as tgt_straight_through_processing_rule_row_md5checksum, 
    rule_id as tgt_rule_id,
    rule_type as tgt_rule_type,
    rule_name as tgt_rule_name, condition_group_number as tgt_condition_group_number, condition_order_number as tgt_condition_order_number,
   straight_through_processing_rule_row_effective_end_datetime as tgt_straight_through_processing_rule_row_effective_end_datetime 
FROM $$reference_schema.straight_through_processing_rules
WHERE straight_through_processing_rule_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
